1. *Spremno* je prihvatio njegovu ponudu. (He readily accepted his offer.)
2. Ona je bez ijedne reči *spremno* izašla iz kuće. (She left the house without a word, ready.)
3. On je *spremno* odgovorio na sva pitanja. (He was ready to answer all the questions.)
4. Ona je *spremno* prihvatila goste. (She welcomed the guests readily.)
5. *Spremno* sam prisustvovao sastanku. (I was present at the meeting, ready.)